snippet.title: William R Fisher Haunted Casino (1997) PC game intro
snippet.description:
Can't really tell you much about the game , it's apparently a casino game with a storyline. From the makers of "Last Half of Darkness" series , Beyond the Spirit's eye , romantic blue etc.

The jerky video is unavoidable. This video shows you some of the area you can walk around.
